Description:
  Creates a single page static site based on a GitHub project.

Example:
  yo sipss

  This will create:
    index.html:                 HTML page with ejs templates replaced by prompt answers

    css/main.css:               Main CSS file associated with index.html
    css/vendor/bulma.min.css:   Bulma v0.71 CSS file

    js/index.js:                Main script used for interacting with index.html

    res/favicon.ico:            Example favicon to be replaced by you
    res/icon-256.png:           Small image used for social media (Twitter / Facebook) cards,
                                  to be replaced by you
    res/screenshot.png:         Main media to be displayed on right-half of site, to
                                  be replaced by you
